{"tid":1436982,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「 終極真。和理非爆機方法!!!! 」","createTime":"2019-08-09T11:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T12:39:35.000Z","uid":107157,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6556502d3baf77eb89bee61cea38dfb9da34c475","tid":1436982,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:54:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">持續性<div style=\"text-align: center;\">零消費</div><div style=\"text-align: right;\">不合作運動</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">呢個活動重點係可以<br />\n工照返，書照讀</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">主要行動</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">建立獨立既經濟網絡，拒絕商店消費，繼續返工</span><br />\n買野同親戚鄰居買，要搭車就比錢叫親戚載，再唔係就搵朋友消費，幫襯小販。千祈唔好幫襯任何要上繳稅收既商鋪。就算真係要消費都以最低既消費代替，例如煮飯食代替出面食。<br />\n工繼續返，不過hea住做! 務求令公司冇生意又要出糧比你!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">作用:</span></span><br />\n1。令政府徵收既消費稅變0<br />\n2。降低公司生意額，間接降低商業稅收<br />\n3。工照返，稅遲交，增加公司負擔同時降低政府稅收<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">再提一提大家，<br />\n政府係對付示威遊行方面洗費已經好大<br />\n啲警犬既加班費更加係火上加油</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強制警犬 WE CONNECT<br />\n你咪試下唔出糧囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"7637b73ab3806a85d2b49d739c2ffa46161a39b9","tid":1436982,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:55:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc6f519d60b21ce4e77326ba65a30fe2063a871","tid":1436982,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c14908864cbe61d3da3